{"word":"G1255 - διαλαλέω - dialaléō - dee-al-al-eh'-o - Commune","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαλαλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dialaléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-al-al-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Commune</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல்லிக்கொள், ஆலோசி"},{"paragraph":"to converse together, to talk with"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G2980 - λαλέω - laléō - lal-eh'-o/2980\">G2980</a>; to <i>talk throughout</i> a company, that is, <i>converse</i> or (generally) <i>publish:</i> - commune, noise abroad.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}